{
  "stem": "11744.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that there were four and a half terrible years of waiting, being scared, being-- being constantly on the defensive, and-- and not trusting anybody-- afraid to talk, afraid to exchange ideas, afraid to telephone.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, this was-- the telephone was the worst weapon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You never could use the telephone because you were taped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, you knew very well that if you had-- if they any idea-- with a husband who had been-- who had been arrested four times, you can imagine that I wasn't-- I wasn't on the list of people who had no involvement.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that the-- all this was-- has to be thought about all the time and be careful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So life was-- I can't describe what life was like, because you-- you were sending a message through a messenger in order not to use the telephone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everything-- everything was for four and a half years like this-- a complete insecurity.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And not knowing what was happening, because the whole thing of the camps-- I mean, the whole-- that nobody ever heard of Auschwitz, nobody ever heard of concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All we knew was that we had to hide the young people, because they were taken for what we called-- what they called the forced-- the labor force.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the labor force that the Germans were taking from every country they invaded, because supposedly, their army and their people were in Russia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were on the Russian front, so they were taking all our young people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so that was one other thing that we had to do-- we had to hide them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to hide them the best we could, so that they wouldn't be taken to send-- to sent in slave labor, forced labor, or whatever they called it.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
